        {
            "title": "陸港股市午後跳水 中國提高投資者證券融資買入保證金最低比例",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在中國股市開年強勢上漲，上證綜指一度靠近4200點之際，中國監管出手降溫以穩住牛市前進腳步，陸港股市周三午後應聲回吐漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據交易所午間發布的公告，1月14日，經中國證監會批准，滬深北交易所將投資者融資買入證券時的融資保證金最低比例從80%提高至100%。此前在2023年8月，三大交易所將該比例從100%降低至80%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">陸港股市主要指數收窄漲幅，其中滬深300指數回到平盤附近，上證綜指當前升約0.1%，此前盤中一度漲超1%。恒生指數當前漲0.3%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b402bf25-5c72-39b5-9278-26dbb540b0c7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國股市近期量價齊升，引發一些投資者對於市場過熱的擔憂。在交易所上調融資保證金最低比例之前，熱門題材商業航天概念相關股票集中提示交易風險，初步顯示監管降溫跡象。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「管理層還是希望慢牛。」群益證券分析師林靜華指出，「最近市場漲的太快，且成交量快速放大。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周前兩個交易日A股成交額連創新高，均超過3.6萬億元人民幣，周二融資餘額也升至約2.67萬億元人民幣的歷史新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B8%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%88%E5%BE%8C%E8%B7%B3%E6%B0%B4-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E8%9E%8D%E8%B3%87%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%A5%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89%E9%87%91%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B-052705421.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 14:15:55",
